FR Abilities











■ Rules for Force Abilities and the Force Gauge

Force abilities and the force gauge operate according to the following rules.

  • During force time, triggered force time effects correspond to the ally who used the force ability.
    *Effects only trigger while that ally present in battle.

  • Remaining turns on force time decrease with ally turns.
    *Turns that do not add to the turn count will decrease force time turns.

  • A force ability can be used one time during burst mode without consuming the force gauge. Force time, however, will not be entered.

  • Force abilities cannot be used during force time.

  • During co-op, the force gauge, force time, and HP damage bonuses are shared with other players.
